text: Jordan Wedderburn (born 30 December 2002) is a South African water polo player. She competed for the South Africa women's national water polo team in the 2019 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * jordan-wedderburn * achievers-of-the-week * netherlands-hungary-greece- australia-move-on-to-womens-wp-quarterfinals Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:South African water polo players
